The article is a proclamation issued by President Donald J. Trump on June 12, 2020, in honor of Flag Day and National Flag Week. The proclamation emphasizes the importance of the American flag as a symbol of unity, sacrifice, and patriotism. It acknowledges the sacrifices made by heroes throughout history, including those fighting the coronavirus pandemic. The proclamation also highlights the significance of Flag Day and National Flag Week, urging all Americans to display the flag and celebrate America's heritage and independence.